#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_CALL_YOUR_HOST"
msgid "If this keeps happening frequently you may want to contact your host about moving your site to a bigger hosting package, or otherwise upgrading your site\'s server."
msgstr "Ako se ovo događa često, možda biste željeli kontaktirati svog hostera radi prelaska na veći hosting paket ili nadogradnje poslužitelja."

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_IOWAIT"
msgid "High I/O Wait (%0.2f%%)"
msgstr "Visoko I/O čekanje (%0.2f%%)"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_IOWAIT_WHAT"
msgid "Your server is spending a lot of time waiting for disk operations, as expressed by the I/O Wait time (it is expressed as a percentage of the total CPU time available). This means that your server\'s storage is struggling to keep up with the demand."
msgstr "Vaš poslužitelj provodi puno vremena čekajući na disk operacije, što je izraženo I/O čekanjem (izraženo kao postotak ukupnog dostupnog CPU vremena). To znači da pohrana vašeg poslužitelja ne može pratiti potražnju."

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_CPU"
msgid "High CPU Utilisation (%0.2f%%)"
msgstr "Visoka iskoristivost CPU-a (%0.2f%%)"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_CPU_WHAT"
msgid "Your server is closing to using its processor (CPU) to the maximum capacity available. This means that your server is struggling under the load."
msgstr "Vaš poslužitelj se bliži maksimalnom kapacitetu procesora (CPU). To znači da je poslužitelj pod velikim opterećenjem."

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_SITE_DISK"
msgid "High Site Disk Usage (%0.2f%%)"
msgstr "Visoka iskoristivost diska web-mjesta (%0.2f%%)"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_COMMON_DISK"
msgid "High Site &amp; Database Disk Usage (%0.2f%%)"
msgstr "Visoka iskoristivost diska web-mjesta i baze podataka (%0.2f%%)"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_SITE_DISK_WHAT"
msgid "Your server\'s storage is almost at capacity. When you exceed this limit you will not be able to create files (including cache and temporary files), leading to your site being unable to function properly."
msgstr "Pohrana vašeg poslužitelja je gotovo pri kapacitetu. Kada prijeđete ovaj limit nećete moći stvarati datoteke (uključujući predmemoriju i privremene datoteke), što će onemogućiti ispravno funkcioniranje vašeg web-mjesta."

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_COMMON_DISK_WHAT"
msgid "Your server\'s storage is almost at capacity. When you exceed this limit you will not be able to perform database operations which delete or create data, you will not be able to create files (including cache and temporary files), leading to your site being unable to function properly."
msgstr "Pohrana vašeg poslužitelja je gotovo pri kapacitetu. Kada prijeđete ovaj limit nećete moći izvoditi operacije na bazi podataka koje brišu ili stvaraju podatke, nećete moći stvarati datoteke, što će onemogućiti ispravno funkcioniranje vašeg web-mjesta."

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_DB_DISK"
msgid "High Database Disk Usage (%0.2f%%)"
msgstr "Visoka iskoristivost diska baze podataka (%0.2f%%)"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SITE_LBL_SERVER_WARN_DB_DISK_WHAT"
msgid "Your server\'s storage is almost at capacity. When you exceed this limit you will not be able to perform database operations which delete or create data, leading to your site being unable to function properly."
msgstr "Pohrana vašeg poslužitelja je gotovo pri kapacitetu. Kada prijeđete ovaj limit nećete moći izvoditi operacije na bazi podataka koje brišu ili stvaraju podatke, što će onemogućiti ispravno funkcioniranje vašeg web-mjesta."

