#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SYSCONFIG_LBL_FIELD_TASKS_COREUPDATE_INSTALL"
msgid "When An Update Is Found"
msgstr "Cuando se encuentra una actualización"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SYSCONFIG_LBL_FIELD_TASKS_COREUPDATE_INSTALL_HELP"
msgid "Do nothing: no action is taken. Send email: An email is sent, nothing is installed. Patch: Only patch versions (e.g. 1.2.<strong>3</strong> to 1.2.<strong>4</strong>) are installed; an email is sent otherwise. Minor: Only patch and minor versions (e.g. 1.<strong>2</strong>.x to 1.<strong>3</strong>.x) are installed; an email is sent otherwise. Any version: installs all updates, even if the major version changes (e.g. <strong>1</strong>.x to <strong>2</strong>.x)."
msgstr "No hacer nada: no se toma ninguna acción. Enviar correo: se envía un correo electrónico, pero no se instala nada. Instalar: se instala la actualización automáticamente."

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SYSCONFIG_LBL_FIELD_TASKS_EXTUPDATE_INSTALL"
msgid "When An Extension Update Is Found"
msgstr "Cuando se encuentra una actualización de extensión"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SYSCONFIG_LBL_FIELD_TASKS_EXTUPDATE_INSTALL_HELP"
msgid "This preference can be overridden for any individual extension below. You can also override this for any individual extension and site in each site\'s configuration page."
msgstr "Esta preferencia puede anularse para cualquier extensión individual. También puede configurarlo por extensión en la tabla de abajo."

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SYSCONFIG_LBL_FIELD_SESSION_TOKEN_ALGORITHM"
msgid "Anti-CSRF Token Algorithm"
msgstr "Algoritam anti-CSRF tokena"

#, phpformat
msgctxt "PANOPTICON_SYSCONFIG_LBL_FIELD_SESSION_TOKEN_ALGORITHM_HELP"
msgid "The hash algorithm for creating an anti-CSRF token. SHA-512 offers the best security, but may not work on some hosts because it\'s very long. MD5 offers the least security but is compatible with all hosts. Only change if you have problems when clicking action buttons in Panopticon."
msgstr "Hash algoritam za stvaranje anti-CSRF tokena. SHA-512 nudi najveću sigurnost, ali možda neće raditi na nekim hostovima jer je previše dugačak. MD5 nudi najmanji sigurnosni nivo."

