msgid "Email addresses from these domains will be blocked from registering. Separate with commas or newlines. Useful for blocking disposable email services."
msgstr "E-mail adrese s ovih domena bit će blokirane od registracije. Odvojite zarezima ili novim recima."

#, phpformat
